HellDwarf: {
	QuestName: Trapped Fire
	QuestDescription: Deep within the Underworld, even the fire feels like it's trying to escape from something. Bring a bottle of hot liquid to the one who watches the ruins.
	QuestStage: Collect Bottled Lava
	QuestProgress0: Thanks for the Bottled Lava. It’s warm, but it doesn't bring any real heat.
	QuestProgress1: I can't even believe that I'm giving tasks to someone in such a terrible place though. Albeit i was sixteen years here. I really need the bottled lava.
	QuestProgress2: You can't get it? No problem. Failure is the only honest thing
	QuestButton: Accept
	QuestButtonGive: Give Bottled Lava
	QuestCompleted: Exactly, thank you so much. Take these magma chunks. They don't breathe, so they won't lie or hurt you.
	QuestCompletedFalse: You don't have an Bottled Lava yet.  Perhaps the flames refused to be contained by someone like you.
}

