HellDwarfQuest_First: {
	QuestName: Pandemonium
	QuestDescription: Deep beneath the Collapsed Bridge lies a relic from the time before the Great Tragedy. A fragment of a world that didn't know it will ever turn in such a terrible place.
	QuestStage: Collect Pandemonium
	QuestProgress0: Thanks for the Pandemonium, i feel like i'm touching a ghost from the past
	QuestProgress1: The bridge collapsed when escape stopped being necessary, and back then, there was no trace of lava below it. There is a locked chest at the bottom, left by those who thought they could hide their past. I need items from there
	QuestProgress2: You can't get it? Yeah, i know it’s hard, the ruins don't like to give up the things they have buried.
	QuestButton: Accept
	QuestButtonGive: Give Pandemonium
	QuestCompleted: Impossible. I can't believe. I can't say I feel relief, but the silence here feels a bit lighter.
	QuestCompletedFalse: You don't have the Pandemonium. The lock remains unbroken yet
}

